      <title>由于盈利疲软引发评级下调，Axis Bank 股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/axis-bank-shares-slump-as-weak-earnings-trigger-downgrades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度银行 Axis Bank Ltd. 股价下跌，原因是其第一季度盈利低于预期，资产质量恶化，信贷成本上升。至少有五家券商下调了该股评级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/axis-bank-shares-slump-as-weak-earnings-trigger-downgrades</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 04:01:45 GMT</pubDate>
